{"tid":1466893,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"對於塞機場有少少睇法","createTime":"2019-08-13T16:59:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T17:03:59.000Z","uid":237143,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e9975e543b82334228ed61715cba5ade3b2f9dff","tid":1466893,"uid":237143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:59:09.000Z","msg":"今日好多post話塞機場會令到外國人觀感變差 <br />\n其實可以唔洗解釋咁多 <br />\n叫佢地搵領事館幫手<br />\n就好似popo面對記者問題都係叫佢地搵返pprb<br />\n領事館官員係一定會比壓力港共政府 叫佢地盡快解決呢單野<br />\n因為對外國人黎講 <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">港共政府先係香港嘅大台!!</span></span><br />\n而港共政府係無可能將呢個波射番出去!!<br />\n因為我地無大台!!<br />\n要善用自身優勢呀各位<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da03bd6aa31df8dc05441efb118fa6ebc175978e","tid":1466893,"uid":237143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:59:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cec03a4cb5949bd71a972efca6abf1e0a181729","tid":1466893,"uid":95487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:00:24.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">求求大家唔好再執著於捉鬼</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n鬼一定有<br />\n唔會捉得晒<br />\n<br />\n我地有<span style=\"color: gold;\">連儂牆</span>，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">撕一貼百</span></span><br />\n<br />\n中共有<span style=\"color: gold;\">防火牆</span>，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">捉一滲百</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">捉鬼唔係重點呀大家<br />\n提醒同路人提防就夠</span></span><br />\n<br />\n利申 其實打鬼/狗並唔反感<br />\n但我唔希望大家係咁既氛圍下打<br />\n好易失去理智，anyway 核爆都唔割<br />\n慶幸我身邊既和理都話星期六會再入機場<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">五大訴求，缺一不可</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<del><span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">題外話，下次唔好咁突然除褲好唔好</span></span></del><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a427c55a98e5ee8c3e5ca6e64168a452fe00c50","tid":1466893,"uid":152085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:01:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"42963ec728eff000738afa242aabf75e8f182f2f","tid":1466893,"uid":237143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:01:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e261f68b633c701c901018ef742844ad7c7fc4ad","tid":1466893,"uid":181535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:01:29.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"8bc5653833fa764afd367e455a176a940cca0a2c","tid":1466893,"uid":237143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:02:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"634b6ae890a7214af4c8eccc593c6497cb1ae7ea","tid":1466893,"uid":237143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:03:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}